      • releaseGracefully

        public void releaseGracefully()
        Releases the association in a graceful way.
        • makes sure the current state is eligible for calling a release() before doing so
        • waits for outstanding RSP before release
        • handles exceptions and logs detected issues
        This method will not throw exceptions normally.
